parameters: I knew you didn't do this!
It's been a long time since anyone's called you that.
Where did you hear my name?
I knew this map was just another way to lure me in.
You talk to me like I know you.
You don't have to come in here like that.
I'm determined to give women equal treatment.
Why don't we treat ourselves to some tea first?
Something feels colder than the usual Satan. ......
I feel like something important is left completely empty.
I'll give you credit for making it through this dungeon.
It's only a test to become my queen.
And now, the carbuncle, the sign of marriage.
If you're going to ask me to marry you, can we do it another time...
You're looking at me in disbelief.
After all, I've been watching you since you entered the dungeon.
You came to deliver me, didn't you?
It is a token of marriage to be presented to my future queen.
That's a good enough trade off.
Let's take the best prize we can get.
I'm not giving you Mr. Car.
Because you locked something in a treasure chest.
You didn't want to come to me, so you ran to me.
It's just a pedestal with a rubelkrak on the forehead, right?
It's ridiculous to walk around with something that troublesome.
Why don't you just get on with it and remove the jewelry?
You've got to be kidding me.
You said something you shouldn't have.
Don't treat me like an object for your own reasons!
I knew it was an impostor of Satan...!
Satan would never say something like this.
Leave the carbuncle and get out of here.
You have a very clear soul...
It will be interesting to see how it ages...
Let's go all the way with them, shall we?
You've got a lot of bone for a human.
I thought you were just a little girl, so I underestimated you a little.
This king of the demon world will do his best to deal with you.
You noticed that during the fight, didn't you?
Now that I think about it, it's really annoying.
The original is a sightseeing tour of the Witches' Forest.
He left his own shadow behind.
More than 100 years ago, as part of the search for a bride.
When I stepped into the Witch's Woods...
He's very fond of the Mage Tower, which stands quietly in the forest.
The tower's plan to become an attraction was opposed.
He created a dungeon beneath the forest and placed his shadow in the deepest part.
Hopefully, someone will challenge the shadows and strike them down.
As usual, the scale of annoyance is huge.
He wasn't with me from the beginning.
I was never instilled with the love of a carbuncle.
If I had love for you.
I'd have to compete with the original for the carbuncle.
I know that feeling all too well.
You were so dignified, so strong...
Even though he was a shadow, the way he stood up to the Demon Lord without fear.
It will be fascinating to watch.
I'd like to have a cup of tea with you when I get a chance.
Thanks for the food. It was delicious.
I don't know, a long time ago.
I remember the first time I met Satan.
I think you're cooler when you're not looking at me...
I'll come back when I feel like it!
That's why you fell in love with the original.
Carbuncle and I are treated equally.
Do ordinary people have the capacity to do that?
You'll feel the same way about the original.
